TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT IN_ST_HSUPGRADE.DEC_RECORD_NO, IN_ST_HSUPGRADE.TXT_SYSTEM_ID, IN_ST_HSUPGRADE.TXT_COMP_CD, IN_ST_HSUPGRADE.TXT_PLY_NO, IN_ST_HSUPGRADE.TXT_LIFE_NO, IN_ST_HSUPGRADE.TXT_COMPONTENT_NO, IN_ST_HSUPGRADE.TXT_COVERAGE_NO, IN_ST_HSUPGRADE.DEC_SEQUENCE_NO, IN_ST_HSUPGRADE.DTE_TXN_DATE, IN_ST_HSUPGRADE.TXT_UPG_AGT, IN_ST_HSUPGRADE.TXT_UPG_AGT_CLIENT, IN_ST_HSUPGRADE.TXT_UPG_AGY, IN_ST_HSUPGRADE.TXT_ORG_AGT, IN_ST_HSUPGRADE.TXT_ORG_AGT_CLIENT, IN_ST_HSUPGRADE.TXT_ORG_AGY, IN_ST_HSUPGRADE.TXT_COVERAGE_ID, IN_ST_HSUPGRADE.TXT_OLD_PLAN_CODE, IN_ST_HSUPGRADE.TXT_NEW_PLAN_CODE, IN_ST_HSUPGRADE.DEC_PREM_INC_PLY, IN_ST_HSUPGRADE.DEC_PREM_INC_LOC, IN_ST_HSUPGRADE.DEC_ORG_PREM_NET_PLY, IN_ST_HSUPGRADE.DEC_ORG_PREM_NET_LOC, IN_ST_HSUPGRADE.DEC_NEW_PREM_NET_PLY, IN_ST_HSUPGRADE.DEC_NEW_PREM_NET_LOC, IN_ST_HSUPGRADE.DEC_ORG_PREM_NET_TOT_PLY, IN_ST_HSUPGRADE.DEC_ORG_PREM_NET_TOT_LOC, IN_ST_HSUPGRADE.DEC_NEW_PREM_NET_TOT_PLY, IN_ST_HSUPGRADE.DEC_NEW_PREM_NET_TOT_LOC, IN_ST_HSUPGRADE.TXT_CURR_CODE, IN_ST_HSUPGRADE.DTE_OLD_COVER_DATE, IN_ST_HSUPGRADE.DTE_NEW_COVER_DATE, IN_ST_HSUPGRADE.DTE_UPD_DATE, IN_ST_HSUPGRADE.DTE_ANN_DATE, IN_ST_HSUPGRADE.DTE_INSERT_DATE, IN_ST_HSUPGRADE.TXT_STATUS, IN_ETL_CONTROL.TXT_FILE_NAME, IN_ETL_CONTROL.TXT_KEY_VALUE, IN_ST_HSUPGRADE.TXT_FHR, IN_ST_HSUPGRADE.TXT_ORPHAN_STATUS FROM IN_ST_HSUPGRADE, IN_ETL_CONTROL WHERE IN_ETL_CONTROL.TXT_KEY_STRING='HSUPGRADE_CYCLE_DATE' AND IN_ETL_CONTROL.DEC_RUNNING_FLG =1

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT CS_POSITION.RULEELEMENTOWNERSEQ as RULEELEMENTOWNERSEQ, CS_POSITION.GENERICATTRIBUTE4 as GENERICATTRIBUTE4, CS_POSITION.NAME as NAME FROM CS_POSITION WHERE islast=1 AND removedate> sysdate

GROUP.DESCRIPTION: Path for the data when none of the group conditions are satisfied.
GROUP.NAME: DEFAULT1

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF(TXT_SYSTEM_ID <>'IL', DECODE(TXT_COMP_CD , '011','SGT'||SUBSTR(TXT_UPG_AGT,LENGTH(TXT_UPG_AGT) - 4,5),'014','BRT'||SUBSTR(TXT_UPG_AGT,LENGTH(TXT_UPG_AGT) - 4,5),ERROR('INVLAID COMPANY CODE:'||TXT_COMP_CD) ) ,DECODE(TXT_COMP_CD,'2' ,'SGT'||SUBSTR(TXT_UPG_AGT,LENGTH(TXT_UPG_AGT) - 4,5),'4','BRT'||SUBSTR(TXT_UPG_AGT,LENGTH(TXT_UPG_AGT) - 4,5),ERROR('INVLAID COMPANY CODE:'||TXT_COMP_CD)))
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: LOOKUP_AGENT

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF (TXT_SYSTEM_ID = 'IL', DECODE(TXT_COMP_CD , '2','SGY'||TXT_UPG_AGY, '4','BRY'||TXT_UPG_AGY,ERROR('INVLAID COMPANY CODE:'||TXT_COMP_CD)), DECODE(TXT_COMP_CD , '011','SGY'||TXT_UPG_AGY, '014','BRY'||TXT_UPG_AGY,ERROR('INVLAID COMPANY CODE:'||TXT_COMP_CD)))
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: LOOKUP_AGENCY

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF(ISNULL(BU_NAME) OR BU_NAME = '' , 'BU NAME NOT FOUND, ','')||IIF(ISNULL(AGY_POS_NAME) OR AGY_POS_NAME = '' , 'AGENCY POSITION CAN BE FOUND ID SYSTEM, ','')||IIF(ISNULL(AGT_POS_NAME) OR AGY_POS_NAME = '' , 'AGENT POSITION CAN BE FOUND ID SYSTEM, ','')
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: ERROR_MSG

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Post SQL
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
UPDATE IN_ETL_CONTROL SET TXT_KEY_VALUE=(SELECT LPAD(TO_CHAR(COUNT(*)),10,'0') FROM IN_ST_HSUPGRADE WHERE TXT_STATUS IS NOT NULL AND TXT_STATUS<>'1'), DTE_UPDATE_DATE=SYSDATE WHERE TXT_KEY_STRING='HSUPGRADE_STAGE_RECORD_COUNT' and DEC_RUNNING_FLG='1';
COMMIT;
